<!doctype html>
<html class="no-js" lang="">

<head>
  {% set tabAboutDesc = 'Portraiture' %}
  {% include 'content/head.jinja2' %}
</head>

<body>
    {% include 'content/header.jinja2' %}
    {% set page = 'portraiture' %}
    {% include 'content/menu.jinja2' %}
    
    <div class="body">
        <h2>Portraiture</h2>
        <p class="typed-paragraph">
          <b>I love taking portraits!</b> It is something special about having someone in front of the camera, be it outside or in my apartment studio in MÃ¶lndal.
          As with the rest of my work I work with both analogue and digital cameras, but I tend to favor analogue if the circumstance and desired 
          style allows for it. I'm available for hire and would love to help you with your next photo project. 
          I'll happily receive any questions at gallery@rahmn.net or at <a class="normal" href="https://www.instagram.com/rahmnphoto/" >@rahmnphoto</a>.
        </p>
        {%for catName, pics in (inventory | sortbycategories).items() %}
        {% if catName == "Portraiture" %}
        <div class="gallery" >{% for pic in pics %}
            <a href="{{pic.view | tolink }}?src=portraiture&stay" id="{{pic.displayname}}" class="image" style="background-color:{{pic.colour}};"   
                data-width="{{pic.medium.width}}" 
                data-height="{{pic.medium.height}}" 
                  data-srcset="
                    {{pic.huge.path | tolink}} {{pic.huge.width}}w,
                    {{pic.large.path | tolink}} {{pic.large.width}}w,
                    {{pic.medium.path | tolink}} {{pic.medium.width}}w"
                  data-src= "{{pic.medium.path | tolink }}"
            >
                <span>{{pic.displayname}} </span>
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <template id="imgTmp">
        <a class="image" >
          <span></span>
          <img></img>
       </a>
    </template>
    {% include 'content/footer.jinja2' %}
    <script>
        document.write('<script src="/js/main.js"><\/script>');
    </script>
</body>
</html>
